#: src/lib/content/sample-content-generator.ts:218
msgid "sample.chapter2.content"
msgstr ""
"🇮🇱 In this second chapter, we explore how content is structured within an "
"EPUB file. The format uses XHTML for text content, CSS for styling, and a "
"manifest to organize all the components that make up a complete digital "
"book."

#: src/lib/content/sample-content-generator.ts:217
msgid "sample.chapter2.title"
msgstr "🇮🇱 Chapter 2: Content Structure"

#: src/lib/content/sample-content-generator.ts:204
